metadata.description:
Title: Be aware of «great ruzzian culture»  
Artist: Martyn Yakub  
Collection: Ruslit  
Token: #1

Ukrainian classic poet Taras Shevchenko is kicking ruzzian poet Aleksandr Pushkin.

Russia spreads its culture worldwide, after spreads its language and after it will bomb your cities to defend its culture and language.
